edu.umass.cs.gnsserver.utils

Class StringVersionedMap<KeyType,ValueType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umass.cs.gnsserver.utils.StringVersionedMap<KeyType,ValueType>
  • Type Parameters:
    KeyType -
    ValueType - 

    public class StringVersionedMap<KeyType,ValueType>
extends Object
    This class implements a specific kind of a trie. The key is a string concatenated with a version number. In addition to get(key) that tries to retrieve an exact match, it supports a match(keyPrefix) method that matches the keyPrefix against the highest versioned key with keyPrefix as a prefix. 'keyPrefix' must have a toString() method but doesn't have to be a String. 'key' must be a String and is computed as keyPrefix.toString()+version.
